timeline.bodyText:
if we had
    To from( TrackerPreheat preheat, From object, To existingInstance );

    default To from( TrackerPreheat trackerPreheat, Function<TrackerPreheat, To> toInstanceProvider, From object )
    {
        To instance = toInstanceProvider.apply( trackerPreheat );
        return from( trackerPreheat, object, instance );
    }

    default List<To> from( TrackerPreheat preheat, List<From> objects )
    {
        return objects
            .stream()
            .map( object -> from( preheat, object ) )
            .collect( Collectors.toList() );
    }

we might remove all implementations of these methods from children classes, whose responsibility would just be to implement:
    To from( TrackerPreheat preheat, From object, To existingInstance );

